{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2956093, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为他们没有子宫", "timestamp": 1637059380, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956107, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956093, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不管有没有，分析一下也知道呀，堕胎（相比于禁止堕胎）是百利而无害的。", "timestamp": 1637059481, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956108, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "生命的起源是受精卵，杀死未出世的胎儿，和杀死已出世的胎儿，本质上的区别在哪？", "timestamp": 1637059486, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956116, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956108, "tag": null, "text": "我倒不是支持禁止堕胎，但一条生命没法为自己发言的时候，真的一点权力都没有，虽然它看见了这世道也不一定愿意被生出来", "timestamp": 1637059544, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956117, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956108, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 堕胎没有使任何*人*的利益受到损害。", "timestamp": 1637059565, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956126, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956116, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 原洞Alice宁来啦", "timestamp": 1637059597, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956127, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956116, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 所以为了满足这个连意识都不一定有得细胞的权利，就要强迫母亲十月怀胎鬼门关走一遭生下来？", "timestamp": 1637059597, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956129, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956116, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 因为那东西还不是*人*。无论任何时候，人大于人以外的东西。", "timestamp": 1637059606, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956135, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956126, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 什么Alice？宁谁啊？", "timestamp": 1637059625, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956136, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "他们生活在前现代。简单理解 就是他们是过去来的时空旅行者。", "timestamp": 1637059627, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956137, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956116, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 受精卵有人权，母亲就没有人权，你凭什么剥夺一个人的人权啊", "timestamp": 1637059637, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956139, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956116, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 而堕胎，这个行为并未使得任何人的利益受损。\n相比之下，我们反对基因编辑，是因为基因编辑真的影响了人。", "timestamp": 1637059643, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956140, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956129, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 支持dz", "timestamp": 1637059645, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956142, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956127, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 看清楚了，我没说禁止堕胎啊", "timestamp": 1637059646, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956145, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956135, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 或许你就是那个不愿意生下来的人。活在这世界上真是委屈你了。", "timestamp": 1637059666, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956149, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956142, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 但是这个讨论很危险。你去跟你妈妈讲，你看你妈妈怎么回答", "timestamp": 1637059688, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956150, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956139, "tag": null, "text": "人从被取出子宫的那一刻才是真正的人，这是你们的看法", "timestamp": 1637059689, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956156, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956145, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 老子爱怎么活怎么活，用不着你来指手画脚，管好你自己", "timestamp": 1637059727, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956162, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956150, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我身上的一颗氢原子，在超过一百亿年以前就存在了，而它最终成为了我的一部分。问题是，它是*人*吗？", "timestamp": 1637059761, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956171, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956162, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 没人说氢原子是生命吧？", "timestamp": 1637059816, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956181, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956171, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 那么，一个负一岁的细胞，和一个负一百亿岁的氢原子，本质上的区别在哪？", "timestamp": 1637059889, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956186, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956162, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你这滑坡滑得狠了点，直接滑出生物界了", "timestamp": 1637059931, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956191, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956186, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 归谬论证就是要狠嘛。", "timestamp": 1637059971, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956193, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956181, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 氢原子它只是氢原子，不会摄取养料，产生废物进行代谢，没有任何生命特征，你告诉我区别在哪？", "timestamp": 1637059994, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956201, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956191, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 步子跨大了，就成了扯淡，何不再狠一点，把原子也打破吧", "timestamp": 1637060047, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956207, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一般认为受精卵神经系统开始发育之后才算是生命的开始吧，而且在这之后堕胎应该会对母亲很危险？", "timestamp": 1637060072, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956217, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956201, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 未出世的胎儿供养都来自于母体，仍然处于依附生存的状态", "timestamp": 1637060131, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956220, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可能会有伦理问题，在于生命的起点，是受精卵，还是出生的胎儿。目前的观点一般认为是前者", "timestamp": 1637060142, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956231, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956201, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 它属于母体的一部分啊", "timestamp": 1637060185, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956245, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956217, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 所以，人为刀俎，我为鱼肉，那么人出世之后相当一段时间仍处于依附父母生存的状态，但如果屠杀儿童，会被认为是反人类的行为。", "timestamp": 1637060251, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956251, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大家的讨论已经超出生物学和医学的范畴了…", "timestamp": 1637060319, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956252, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956245, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 首先要虐杀母体的胎儿，首先是伤害母体有罪，其次，你出了母体，有人要害你是有罪", "timestamp": 1637060320, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956257, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956245, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 你好杠啊", "timestamp": 1637060326, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956270, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956193, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 一个氢原子，后来组成了一条DNA，然后DNA又进入了卵细胞，二十几年之后受精了成为受精卵，然后逐渐地变成了一坨肉球，然后长出了各个器官，最后成为了一个人。\n在这个过程中，它从“完全不是人”到“完全是人”之间的过渡是连续的。为什么你认为，从受精卵开始它就算人了呢？", "timestamp": 1637060399, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956273, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956245, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 偷换概念", "timestamp": 1637060417, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956276, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956257, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你说我杠，洞主直接滑出生物界拿氢原子反驳不是更杠？", "timestamp": 1637060456, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956288, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956276, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: “归谬论证”指的是，用你的论述方法能得到显著不正确的结论，所以你的论证是错的。", "timestamp": 1637060531, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956302, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "觉得没出yd的胎儿就不是人的观点，建议发公网讨论。", "timestamp": 1637060647, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956306, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956270, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我这样认为的理由是它在那一时刻组成了完整的细胞，即构成生物体的基本单位，在那之前它称不上是生物。这个过程确实是连续的，但就在那一刻完成了无生命到有生命的转折。", "timestamp": 1637060663, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956310, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956276, "tag": null, "text": "设 X 是一个行为。我们支持 X 的充分条件是，经过 X，每个人都没有受损。我们反对 X 的必要条件是，经过 X，存在一个人的利益受损。", "timestamp": 1637060689, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956312, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956288, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那么请论证你用的是我的论述方法。", "timestamp": 1637060701, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956330, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956312, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 你们停一停。权利不是辩论出来的。", "timestamp": 1637060782, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956335, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956312, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 依法治国了。有主张 去选人大代表。", "timestamp": 1637060819, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956344, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956335, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 没兴趣，让洞主去吧", "timestamp": 1637060868, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956348, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956312, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 要么你能首先给出有效的反驳，要么我会要求你对你所说的每一句话——精确到每个逗号——论证它确实成立。", "timestamp": 1637060875, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956358, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956348, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 何必浪费时间说明法律现实中都成立的权利的合法性。", "timestamp": 1637060929, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956366, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956348, "tag": null, "text": "我的观点就是，一个人被称为一个人首先从受精卵开始，洞主的意见是从婴儿开始，而洞主用氢原子来反驳我，他认为我的逻辑就是简单粗暴地把一个东西拆成组成部分，所以他接着拆，拆出了生物的范畴，我认为这是强拆。", "timestamp": 1637061004, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956393, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956366, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 除非你有权力废止这项权利 否则你论证再精妙也没用啊", "timestamp": 1637061222, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956395, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为他们是男的", "timestamp": 1637061225, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956429, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": 2956395, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 不要搞男女对立嘛。我也是男的。在这个问题里面性别不是本质问题，本质的问题是受精卵算不算人……", "timestamp": 1637061370, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2956695, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "受精卵要是算人，那你的存在还杀死了两条生命呢……毕竟同卵双胞胎就是你一个人裂出来的两条生命……原洞alice什么傻逼", "timestamp": 1637063987, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2960907, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "胎儿不是人，就像病毒不是生命。\n胎儿不能脱离母体而活，就像病毒不能脱离细胞而活。\n\n新生儿是独立的人，拥有人权，因为他们脱离母体可以存活了。\n胎儿不是，胎儿不能脱离母体存活，所以胎儿更接近母亲的一个器官或者肿瘤（都是活细胞，但是脱离身体就会死），而不是一个独立的“人”。\n\n而有些非蠢即坏的人总是在刻意忽略的一点是——母亲是人，母亲有完整的人权。女性对自己的人生和自己的某一团细胞享有处置的权力。", "timestamp": 1637098008, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2963040, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 561181, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "bob真的好强，居然敢给人下定义", "timestamp": 1637125485, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 14, "pid": 561181, "reply": 53, "tag": null, "text": "难以理解，为什么会有人反对孕妇有权堕胎……", "timestamp": 1637059367, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1637125486, "url": "", "vote": {}}}